com.polarion.alm.shared.api.utils.charts

Interface PolarionChartBuilder


  • public interface PolarionChartBuilder
    High level API for creating charts. It explicitly and implicitly depends on Highchart API. Clients can use it for rapid chart defining. For fine tuning use HighchartBuilder that can be received by calling build() method.
    Since:
    3.9.0
